data.description: **WOW** BIG Price Reduction - Seller will also help with some CLOSING COSTS!! Don't wait, take a look now! Huge PAID-OFF SOLAR system!! Welcome home to Pioneer Road in the desirable area of Apple Valley on almost a half acre. The front yard is rock-scaped to save on your water bill and has an oversized driveway leading to the RV parking in the backyard. This home features a new HVAC system and a new water softening system to combat the local hard water and utilize all of its many benefits! The large tiled fireplace is the centerpiece for the open and bright living room as you enter this home. The charming kitchen is next to the dining room and includes a new reverse osmosis water system that is plumbed to the sink and as well as  directly to the included refrigerator. Also included in the kitchen are wood cabinets, ceramic tile countertops,  gas stove and a kitchen island featuring a trash compactor. All the bedrooms are spacious and have ceiling fans with lights. The full guest bathroom has a shower-in-tub combo, tile flooring and wood cabinets. The laundry area is inside and includes overhead cabinets for storage. The primary bedroom is double the regular size; you have to see to appreciate it! It has three closets, and an en suite bathroom with a double sink vanity and a privacy door for the toilet area. The garage is finished with drywall material. In the backyard there is a large covered patio - and the concrete extends even further, just waiting for the new owner to create an even larger shaded area for more outdoor living space! This is a great starter home on a large lot. Don’t hesitate, go see it today!
